ru.ifmo.ctddev.belonogov.implementor

Class Main

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.ifmo.ctddev.belonogov.implementor.Main
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    info.kgeorgiy.java.advanced.implementor.Impler, info.kgeorgiy.java.advanced.implementor.JarImpler

    public class Main
extends Object
implements info.kgeorgiy.java.advanced.implementor.JarImpler
    The class represent implementation of interface JarImpler interface. It can generate implementation (the .java file) for classes or interfaces except generic classes. New class args consist of the args class that is implemented plus "Impl" suffix. This class can generate .jar file with generated class.

    This class can throw ImplerException if it's impossible to generate implementation.
